devdoc.author: Set Protocol Wrap adapter for one time token migration that returns data for wrapping LEND into AAVE

params._lendToAaveMigrationProxy: Address of Aave migration contract proxy

returns._0: address        Address of the contract to approve tokens to

returns._1: uint256              Total quantity of wrapped token units to unwrap. This will always be 0 for unwrapping

params._underlyingToken: Address of the component to be wrapped
params._underlyingUnits: Total quantity of underlying units to wrap

returns._1: uint256              Total quantity of underlying units (if underlying is ETH)
